<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>血腥屠戮——卡斯特尔酒店谜团</strong><br />
<strong>Bloody Slaughter - A Mystery in Castell Hotel</strong><br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609819589" alt="TimeElapsed" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;">TimeElapsed</a></span></p>
<p>没错，我想到了<a href="/michael-the-kiler">撒手michael</a>。</p>
<p>最让人摸不着头脑的事情莫过于这位不好惹的主的照片被人挂起来婊。</p>
<p>所以他回来了，以一种无比血腥的方式。</p>
<p>图片由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maki-hisane" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2950163); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2950163&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609819589" alt="maki_hisane" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2950163)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maki-hisane" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2950163); return false;">maki_hisane</a></span>在画廊中提供，遵循CC-BY-SA 3.0协议。</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+72</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
